# Parse4CN1 - Codename One Library for [Parse](https://parse.com) #

**Ths library is a port of Parse's [REST API](https://www.parse.com/docs/rest) to [CodenameOne](http://www.codenameone.com/) (and by extension to Java).** 

## Useful links ##
* [Information about the library, Parse REST API coverage, how to contribute, etc.](https://github.com/sidiabale/parse4cn1#parse4cn1---codename-one-library-for-parse)
* [Javadoc for parse4cn1](http://sidiabale.github.io/parse4cn1/javadoc)
